{"data":[{"date":"07:16 27/06","title":"Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau tr\u1eadn HAGL 4-0 Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh: D\u1ea5u \u1ea5n Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n To\u00e0n","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/27/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-hagl-40-quang-ninh-dau-an-nguyen-van-toan.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u thu\u1ed9c v\u00f2ng 16 V-League 2016, CLB HAGL \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea3 xong m\u00f3n n\u1ee3 \u0111\u00e3 vay tr\u01b0\u1edbc Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh b\u1eb1ng th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i \u0111\u1eadm 4-0 t\u1ea1i Pleiku. V\u00e0 d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd trong tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y.</h2><h2>1. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng V\u0103n To\u00e0n<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ph\u1ea3i g\u1eb7p m\u1ed9t th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c l\u1edbn mang t\u00ean Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 16 V-League, tuy nhi\u00ean c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 HAGL \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng t\u1ef1 tin v\u00e0 s\u1edbm c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng ngay ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 3 c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u nh\u1edd t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o V\u0103n To\u00e0n. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1eeb \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ph\u1ea5t b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00fang t\u1ea7m c\u1ee7a Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng, V\u0103n To\u00e0n v\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng b\u1ee9t t\u1ed1c nh\u01b0 c\u1ed7 xe \u0111ua c\u00f4ng th\u1ee9c 1 \u0111\u00e3 lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n s\u1ef1 \u0111eo b\u00e1m c\u1ee7a h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u0103ng xu\u1ed1ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m l\u1ea1nh l\u00f9ng m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 cho HAGL.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"5 \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau tr\u1eadn HAGL 4-0 Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh D\u1ea5u \u1ea5n V\u0103n To\u00e0n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"5 \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau tr\u1eadn HAGL 4-0 Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh D\u1ea5u \u1ea5n V\u0103n To\u00e0n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/27/1528076018_4.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>V\u0103n To\u00e0n l\u00e0 g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt nh\u1ea5t trong tr\u1eadn&nbsp;</em><i>HAGL 4-0 Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh</i></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00cdt ph\u00fat sau \u0111\u00f3, V\u0103n To\u00e0n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c cho th\u1ea5y t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 l\u1ee3i h\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh khi bu\u1ed9c D\u01b0\u01a1ng Thanh H\u00e0o ph\u1ea3i ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh, khi\u1ebfn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf r\u1eddi s\u00e2n. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u01a1i h\u01a1n ng\u01b0\u1eddi, V\u0103n To\u00e0n v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng g\u1eb7p nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u00eam 3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng n\u1eefa. Qua \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111ang x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 2 tr\u00ean BXH V-League 2018.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i, V\u0103n To\u00e0n ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 chi\u1ebfc ch\u00eca kh\u00f3a m\u1edf ra chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng cho HAGL \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y v\u00e0 n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 anh, ch\u01b0a ch\u1eafc &lsquo;G\u1ed7&rsquo; \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i \u0111\u1eadm \u0111\u00e0 nh\u01b0 v\u1eady.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>2. C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi pha s\u00fat ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1eb9p m\u1eaft \u0111\u01b0a b\u00f3ng ghim th\u1eb3ng v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi CLB Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00e3 s\u01b0u t\u1eadp cho m\u00ecnh 7 pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m nay. T\u00ednh t\u1edbi l\u00fac n\u00e0y C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111ang l\u00e0 ch\u00e2n s\u00fat n\u1ed9i ghi nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng nh\u1ea5t V-League, b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Nguy\u1ec5n Ti\u1ebfn Linh c\u1ee7a B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 c\u00f2n k\u00e9m xa th\u00e0nh t\u00edch ghi b\u00e0n c\u1ee7a Oseni (CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i) nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00e2ng cao th\u00e0nh t\u00edch ghi b\u00e0n c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Cong Phuong HAGL vs Than Quang Ninh\" title=\"C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng HAGL vs Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/27/1523280831_5.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng \u1edf tr\u1eadn HAGL vs Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vi\u1ec7c C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1i HAGL c\u0169ng l\u00e0 tin vui v\u1edbi HLV Park Hang Seo khi m\u00e0 trong th\u00e2m t\u00e2m \u00f4ng r\u1ea5t tin t\u01b0\u1edfng ch\u00e2n s\u00fat x\u1ee9 Ngh\u1ec7 v\u00e0 \u0111ang k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng anh s\u1ebd l\u00e0 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o n\u00ean th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018 v\u00e0 xa h\u01a1n l\u00e0 AFF Cup 2018.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>3. Ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 m\u1ea3nh \u0111\u1ea5t \u0111i d\u1ec5, kh\u00f3 v\u1ec1 v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m nay, CLB HAGL \u0111ang duy tr\u00ec th\u00e0nh t\u00edch 4 th\u1eafng, 2 h\u00f2a v\u00e0 1 b\u1ea1i tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0. \u0110\u00e2y r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u00e0nh t\u00edch kh\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi HAGL d\u00f9 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n khi c\u00e1c tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t g\u1eb7p ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng 4-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh c\u0169ng l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a b\u1ea7u \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Phan Thanh H\u00f9ng \u1edf m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng n\u0103m nay. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, HAGL v\u1edbi tinh th\u1ea7n l\u00ean cao t\u1eebng h\u1ea1 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u00f9ng M\u1ecf v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 5-0 t\u1ea1i c\u00fap qu\u1ed1c gia 2018.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngo\u00e0i s\u1ef1 quen thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n s\u00e2n b\u00e3i c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 s\u1ef1 \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a NHM, m\u1eadt \u0111\u1ed9 kh\u00f4ng kh\u00ed lo\u00e3ng t\u1ea1i Pleiku c\u0169ng l\u00e0 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng h\u1ee5t h\u01a1i khi t\u1edbi ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai thi \u0111\u1ea5u. \u0110\u00f3 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n khi\u1ebfn Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc HAGL \u1edf v\u00f2ng n\u00e0y d\u00f9 h\u1ecd m\u1edbi v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua HAGL tr\u00ean s\u00e2n C\u1ea9m Ph\u1ea3 \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y ch\u01b0a l\u00e2u.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>4. HAGL \u0111ang t\u1ed1t d\u1ea7n l\u00ean v\u1edbi d\u00e0n n\u1ed9i binh<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e1 ch\u1ea5p T\u00e2y \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y khi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng 100% c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u1ed9i, tuy nhi\u00ean c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 HAGL \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch t\u1edbi t\u1eeb v\u00f9ng \u0110\u00f4ng B\u1eafc.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 l\u1edbn, l\u00fac n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 n\u00fai \u0111ang s\u1edf h\u1eefu m\u1ed9t l\u1ee9a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea7y t\u00e0i n\u0103ng v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin. D\u00f9 h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 v\u1eabn \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 trong nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1eeba qua song m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y r\u00f5 l\u00e0 c\u00e1c ng\u00f4i sao tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng HAGL \u0111ang ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh h\u01a1n. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng, Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng, Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng li\u00ean t\u1ee5c l\u1eadp si\u00eau ph\u1ea9m ghi b\u00e0n t\u1ea1i V-League, trong khi \u0111\u00f3 V\u0103n To\u00e0n hay V\u0103n Thanh v\u1eabn cho th\u1ea5y t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9, s\u1ef1 kh\u00e9o l\u00e9o trong c\u00e1c t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng l\u00ean b\u00f3ng. R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng v\u1edbi l\u1ee9a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y, HAGL c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ee7 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ti\u1ebfn xa t\u1ea1i V-League v\u00e0 th\u1eadm ch\u00ed l\u00e0 m\u01a1 m\u1ed9ng ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HAGL\" title=\"HAGL\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/26/Untitled-8-3819-1530018573.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>D\u00e0n n\u1ed9i binh c\u1ee7a HAGL \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t d\u1ea7n l\u00ean qua t\u1eebng tr\u1eadn</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>5. Cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua t\u1ed1p 3 c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, HAGL \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean x\u1ebfp \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 6 tr\u00ean BXH v\u1edbi 23 \u0111i\u1ec3m. L\u00fac n\u00e0y kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch gi\u1eefa h\u1ecd v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u1ed1p 3 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n l\u00e0 2 \u0111i\u1ec3m. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">X\u1ebfp tr\u00ean HAGL l\u00fac n\u00e0y l\u00e0 Thanh H\u00f3a, Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a v\u00e0 Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh v\u1edbi c\u00f9ng 25 \u0111i\u1ec3m, c\u00f2n H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i l\u00fac n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecf xa nh\u00f3m b\u00e1m \u0111u\u1ed5i t\u1edbi 13 \u0111i\u1ec3m d\u00f9 h\u1ecd v\u1eabn c\u00f2n m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea5u. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch n\u0103m nay g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 ng\u00e3 ng\u0169 khi H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i qu\u00e1 m\u1ea1nh v\u1edbi ph\u1ea7n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i song cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua v\u00e0o t\u1ed1p 3 \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh huy ch\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1eabn di\u1ec5n ra r\u1ea5t c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng. L\u00fac n\u00e0y nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ed1p 3 tr\u00ean BXH v\u00e0 c\u00f3 l\u1ebd k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 chung cu\u1ed9c s\u1ebd ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0o s\u1ef1 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i.&nbsp;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>Video: HAGL 4-0 Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh&nbsp;(V\u00f2ng 16 V-League 2018)</em></p>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/6/26/HAGL-4-0-Quang-Ninh.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/hagl-vs-quang-ninh-vong-16-vleague-2018-372-189604.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/26/ket-qua-hagl-vs-quang-ninh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/hagl-vs-quang-ninh-vong-16-vleague-2018-372-189604.html\">HAGL 4-0 Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh (KT): Si\u00eau ph\u1ea9m s\u00fat ph\u1ea1t c\u1ee7a C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap c\u1ee7a V\u0103n To\u00e0n</span><br>\r\nCLB ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh kh\u00f4ng ngo\u1ea1i binh v\u00e0 to\u00e0n h\u00e0ng c\u00e2y nh\u00e0 l\u00e1 v\u01b0\u1eddn \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng khi ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh \u1edf v\u00f2ng 16 V-League 2018. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed,...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3844","checkdouble":"189697"},{"date":"07:21 27/06","title":"HLV Phan Thanh H\u00f9ng b\u1ee9c x\u00fac v\u1edbi tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i b\u1eaft tr\u1eadn HAGL 4-0 Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/13/hlv-phan-thanh-hung-buc-xuc-voi-trong-tai-bat-tran-hagl-40-than-quang-ninh.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn, v\u1ecb thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh HLV Phan Thanh H\u00f9ng \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecf ra th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng khi tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng thi\u00ean v\u1ecb ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 HAGL.</h2><h2>HLV Phan Thanh H\u00f9ng b\u1ee9c x\u00fac v\u1edbi tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i \u1edf tr\u1eadn HAGL vs Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chi\u1ec1u ng\u00e0y 26/6, CLB HAGL c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 g\u1eb7p c\u00e1c v\u1ecb kh\u00e1ch t\u1edbi t\u1eeb Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh. Nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ea7y t\u1ef1 tin, &ldquo;G\u1ed7&rdquo; s\u1edbm c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc sau pha t\u0103ng t\u1ed1c c\u1ee7a V\u0103n To\u00e0n \u1edf ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 3 c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Phan Thanh H\u00f9ng b\u1ee9c x\u00fac v\u1edbi tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i b\u1eaft tr\u1eadn HAGL 4-0 Than  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Phan Thanh H\u00f9ng b\u1ee9c x\u00fac v\u1edbi tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i b\u1eaft tr\u1eadn HAGL 4-0 Than  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/13/hlv-phan-thanh-hung-khang-dinh-ha-noi-se-vo-dich.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV Phan Thanh H\u00f9ng cho r\u1eb1ng tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i thi\u00ean v\u1ecb ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 HAGL</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng s\u1edbm, HAGL thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ef1 tin h\u01a1n v\u00e0 h\u1ecd su\u00fdt c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 hai sau pha b\u1ee9t t\u1ed1c c\u1ee7a V\u0103n To\u00e0n. \u1ede t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng n\u00e0y, s\u1ef1 nhanh nh\u1eb9n c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2n s\u00fat qu\u00ea H\u1ea3i D\u01b0\u01a1ng bu\u1ed9c h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 D\u01b0\u01a1ng Thanh H\u00e0o ph\u1ea3i ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i d\u1eabn t\u1edbi t\u1ea5m th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u00fat ra b\u1edfi tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i Nguy\u1ec5n Ng\u1ecdc Ch\u00e2u.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u1ecb d\u1eabn b\u00e0n tr\u01b0\u1edbc, l\u1ea1i ph\u1ea3i thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi 10 ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00f4ng b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd khi Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb v\u1ee1 tr\u1eadn sau \u0111\u00f3 v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i chung cu\u1ed9c 0-4. Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u trong bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o, HLV Phan Thanh H\u00f9ng \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecf ra th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u1edbi c\u00e1ch c\u1ea7m c\u00f2i c\u1ee7a v\u1ecb vua \u00e1o \u0111en \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay. T\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng c\u1ee7a Thanh H\u00e0o kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ebfn n\u1ed7i ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf. \u0110\u00f3 ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng tranh ch\u1ea5p b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng. C\u00f2n pha b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng khi\u1ebfn Thanh Hi\u1ec1n ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, theo t\u00f4i th\u00ec c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a HAGL c\u1ea7n nh\u1eadn th\u1ebb ph\u1ea1t. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng b\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i m\u1ea5t c\u1eb7p trung v\u1ec7 do th\u1ebb ph\u1ea1t v\u00e0 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u00ean thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t. HAGL thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn 1 chi\u1ec1u. Kh\u00ed h\u1eadu \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y c\u0169ng khi\u1ebfn ch\u00fang t\u00f4i g\u1eb7p nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n...&quot;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc HAGL, Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb t\u1ee5t xu\u1ed1ng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 4 tr\u00ean BXH, x\u1ebfp sau Thanh H\u00f3a v\u00e0 Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a, c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 c\u00f9ng 25 \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u01b0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ea5t M\u1ecf nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u00ean v\u1ec1 hi\u1ec7u s\u1ed1 ph\u1ee5. N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng s\u1edbm tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i trong nh\u1eefng v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi, r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ed1p 3 v\u1edbi th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Phan Thanh H\u00f9ng khi <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/vleague-c291-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">V-League 2018</span> h\u1ea1 m\u00e0n c\u0169ng kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh hi\u1ec7n th\u1ef1c.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-hagl-40-quang-ninh-dau-an-nguyen-van-toan-168-189697.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/27/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-hagl-40-quang-ninh-dau-an-nguyen-van-toan.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-hagl-40-quang-ninh-dau-an-nguyen-van-toan-168-189697.html\">Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau tr\u1eadn HAGL 4-0 Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh: D\u1ea5u \u1ea5n Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n To\u00e0n</span><br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u thu\u1ed9c v\u00f2ng 16 V-League 2016, CLB HAGL \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea3 xong m\u00f3n n\u1ee3 \u0111\u00e3 vay tr\u01b0\u1edbc Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh b\u1eb1ng th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i \u0111\u1eadm 4-0 t\u1ea1i Pleiku. V\u00e0 d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-hagl-vs-quang-ninh-325-189652.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/26/clip-ban-thang-hagl-vs-quang-ninh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-hagl-vs-quang-ninh-325-189652.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: HAGL 4-0 Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh (V\u00f2ng 16 V-League 2018)</span><br>\r\nCLB ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh kh\u00f4ng ngo\u1ea1i binh v\u00e0 to\u00e0n h\u00e0ng c\u00e2y nh\u00e0 l\u00e1 v\u01b0\u1eddn \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng khi ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh \u1edf v\u00f2ng 16 V-League 2018. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed,...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3843","checkdouble":"189698"},{"date":"07:26 27/06","title":"HLV HAGL chia s\u1ebb b\u00ed quy\u1ebft gi\u00fap h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/26/hlv-hagl-chia-se-bi-quyet-giup-hoc-tro-danh-bai-than-quang-ninh.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u di\u1ec5n ra chi\u1ec1u t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 26/6, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean si\u00eau ph\u1ea9m \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh. V\u00e0 HLV D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec7n n\u00e0y?</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u thu\u1ed9c v\u00f2ng 16 V-League di\u1ec5n ra chi\u1ec1u t\u1ed1i 26/6, CLB HAGL c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn t\u00e1i \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 nhi\u1ec1u duy\u00ean n\u1ee3 Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh. \u1ede l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i cay \u0111\u1eafng 0-3, tuy nhi\u00ean \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e8 b\u1eb9p \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 \u0111\u1eadm 4-0.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><em><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV HAGL chia s\u1ebb b\u00ed quy\u1ebft gi\u00fap h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV HAGL chia s\u1ebb b\u00ed quy\u1ebft gi\u00fap h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/26/Untitled-8-3819-1530018573.jpg\"></em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 HAGL c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u hay tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, HLV HAGL D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh t\u1ecf ra r\u1ea5t h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1ec1 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2. &quot;H\u00f4m nay, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed ch\u01a1i d\u1ea1t bi\u00ean \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng cho V\u0103n To\u00e0n. Nh\u00ecn chung, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 nh\u01b0 Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng, V\u0103n To\u00e0n, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t&rdquo;, \u00f4ng Ninh t\u00e2m s\u1ef1.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eb9p m\u1eaft m\u00e0 C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t, HLV D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 b\u00ed quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean ghi b\u00e0n tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ecb n\u00e0y chia s\u1ebb th\u00eam: &ldquo;Sau m\u1ed7i bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng lu\u00f4n \u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1eadp s\u00fat ph\u1ea1t n\u00ean t\u00f4i c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2. V\u1edbi 2 tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp n\u00e0y, t\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 s\u1ebd t\u1ef1 tin \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3&nbsp;k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3&nbsp;t\u1ed1t s\u1eafp t\u1edbi&rdquo;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u00f3i th\u00eam v\u1ec1 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 ngo\u1ea1i binh, v\u1ecb thuy\u1ec3n tr\u01b0\u1edfng HAGL kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Osmar d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, c\u00f2n tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p c\u1ee7a Rimario nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thay b\u1eb1ng m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, HAGL \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng 6 tr\u00ean BXH v\u1edbi 23 \u0111i\u1ec3m. \u1ede v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh s\u1ebd c\u00f3 chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ea7y s\u00f3ng gi\u00f3 t\u1edbi s\u00e2n Tam K\u1ef3 g\u1eb7p nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 Qu\u1ea3ng Nam. V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c HAGL th\u01b0\u1eddng thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t tr\u00ean s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch, \u0111\u00e2y ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch s\u00f3ng gi\u00f3 v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-hagl-40-quang-ninh-dau-an-nguyen-van-toan-168-189697.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/27/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-hagl-40-quang-ninh-dau-an-nguyen-van-toan.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-hagl-40-quang-ninh-dau-an-nguyen-van-toan-168-189697.html\">Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau tr\u1eadn HAGL 4-0 Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh: D\u1ea5u \u1ea5n Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n To\u00e0n</span><br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u thu\u1ed9c v\u00f2ng 16 V-League 2016, CLB HAGL \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea3 xong m\u00f3n n\u1ee3 \u0111\u00e3 vay tr\u01b0\u1edbc Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh b\u1eb1ng th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i \u0111\u1eadm 4-0 t\u1ea1i Pleiku. V\u00e0 d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-phan-thanh-hung-buc-xuc-voi-trong-tai-bat-tran-hagl-40-than-quang-ninh-168-189698.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/13/hlv-phan-thanh-hung-buc-xuc-voi-trong-tai-bat-tran-hagl-40-than-quang-ninh.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-phan-thanh-hung-buc-xuc-voi-trong-tai-bat-tran-hagl-40-than-quang-ninh-168-189698.html\">HLV Phan Thanh H\u00f9ng b\u1ee9c x\u00fac v\u1edbi tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i b\u1eaft tr\u1eadn HAGL 4-0 Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn, v\u1ecb thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh HLV Phan Thanh H\u00f9ng \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecf ra th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng khi tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng thi\u00ean v\u1ecb ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-hagl-vs-quang-ninh-325-189652.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/26/clip-ban-thang-hagl-vs-quang-ninh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-hagl-vs-quang-ninh-325-189652.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: HAGL 4-0 Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh (V\u00f2ng 16 V-League 2018)</span><br>\r\nCLB ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh kh\u00f4ng ngo\u1ea1i binh v\u00e0 to\u00e0n h\u00e0ng c\u00e2y nh\u00e0 l\u00e1 v\u01b0\u1eddn \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng khi ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh \u1edf v\u00f2ng 16 V-League 2018. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed,...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3842","checkdouble":"189699"},{"date":"20:56 26/06","title":"CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C: X\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Nainggolan","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/26/chinh-thuc-xac-dinh-ben-do-moi-cua-nainggolan.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, b\u00e1o ch\u00ed Italia \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i th\u00f4ng tin ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Radja Nainggolan gia nh\u1eadp Inter Milan t\u1eeb CLB AS Roma.\r\n</h2><h2><strong><br>\r\nNainggolan chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Inter<br>\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo \u0111\u00f3, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e3 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 4 n\u0103m v\u1edbi Inter Milan, khi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng Champions League sau 6 n\u0103m v\u1eafng b\u00f3ng. Theo \u0111\u00f3, m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 c\u1ee7a anh ch\u1ec9 r\u1eddi v\u00e0o kho\u1ea3ng 21 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, nh\u01b0ng Inter s\u1ebd c\u00e1c th\u00eam cho Roma 2 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 l\u00e0 Davide Santon v\u00e0 Nicolo Zaniolo.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 Roma \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00e1n ng\u1ea5y th\u00f3i v\u00f4 k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt c\u1ee7a Radja Nainggolan, v\u00e0 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ea9y anh \u0111i ngay m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Serie A \u0111\u1ec3 chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Premier League, v\u00e0 anh \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn Inter thay v\u00ec Juventus.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 m\u1edbi b\u01b0\u1edbc sang tu\u1ed5i 30 cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;T\u00ecnh c\u1ea3m c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f3ng vai tr\u00f2 r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi m\u1ed7i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u00f3 ngh\u0129a c\u00e1c C\u0110V Inter c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec7t t\u00ecnh, gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 t\u00f4i.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C Radja Nainggolan gia nh\u1eadp Inter Milan v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 b\u00e8o h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C Radja Nainggolan gia nh\u1eadp Inter Milan v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 b\u00e8o h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/26/WelcomeNinja-Radja-Nainggolan-unveiled-at-Inter-Milan.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Radja Nainggolan gia nh\u1eadp Inter Milan</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Hy v\u1ecdng ch\u00fang ta c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1eadn h\u01b0\u1edfng kho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac c\u00f9ng nhau. T\u00f4i r\u1ea5t \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi HLV Spalletti, m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i l\u00e0 d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng \u1ea5y, v\u00e0 b\u00e2y gi\u1edd ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u00e1i h\u1ee3p, t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t vui v\u00ec \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;L\u00fd do t\u00f4i l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn Inter Milan l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 tin t\u01b0\u1edfng. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cu\u1ed9c g\u1ecdi t\u1eeb Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c Ausilio, HLV v\u00e0 Zanetti. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 b\u1ecdn h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ec1u khi\u1ebfn t\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y quan tr\u1ecdng, v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn n\u00e0y di\u1ec5n ra r\u1ea5t nhanh ch\u00f3ng, \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng cho b\u01b0\u1edbc ti\u1ebfp theo c\u1ee7a cu\u1ed9c phi\u00eau l\u01b0u.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;M\u1ed9t th\u00f4ng \u0111i\u1ec7p g\u1eedi t\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 \u01b0? T\u00f4i v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i hi\u1ec3u r\u00f5 b\u1ecdn h\u1ecd, nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t vui m\u1eebng v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 ch\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3n t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y. Hy v\u1ecdng c\u00e1c C\u0110V c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng theo c\u00e1ch t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m t\u1ed1t \u1edf Serie A v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 Champions League. Inter Milan c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t l\u1ecbch s\u1eed \u0111\u1eb1ng sau, v\u00e0 gi\u1edd l\u00e0 l\u00fac ch\u00fang ta tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u00e2u \u00c2u.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Radja Nainggolan gia nh\u1eadp Inter Milan, CLB Roma \u0111\u00e3 ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Javier Pastore t\u1eeb PSG v\u1ec1 th\u1ebf ch\u1ed7.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/chinh-thuc-emre-can-gia-nhap-juventus-176-189191.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/21/chinh-thuc-emre-can-gia-nhap-juventus.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/chinh-thuc-emre-can-gia-nhap-juventus-176-189191.html\">CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C: Emre Can gia nh\u1eadp Juventus d\u01b0\u1edbi d\u1ea1ng CNTD</span><br>\r\n\u00cdt ph\u00fat tr\u01b0\u1edbc, th\u00f4ng tin ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Emre Can gia nh\u1eadp Juventus ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c s\u1ebd gia nh\u1eadp CLB Italia v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ef1 do.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/nong-roma-chinh-thuc-hot-tay-tren-muc-tieu-cua-mu-176-188276.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/12/nong-roma-chinh-thuc-hot-tay-tren-muc-tieu-cua-mu.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/nong-roma-chinh-thuc-hot-tay-tren-muc-tieu-cua-mu-176-188276.html\">N\u00d3NG: Roma CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C h\u1edbt tay tr\u00ean m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a M.U</span><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Rome \u0111\u00e3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng sao tr\u1ebb Justin Kluivert, con trai c\u1ee7a c\u1ef1u danh th\u1ee7 Patrick Kluivert t\u1eeb Ajax v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 21 tri\u1ec7u \u0111\u00f4la.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3841","checkdouble":"189657"},{"date":"18:59 26/06","title":"K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 HAGL vs Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f2ng 16 V-League 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/26/clip-ban-thang-hagl-vs-quang-ninh.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chuy\u00ean trang Bongda24h c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt chi ti\u1ebft k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 HAGL vs Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f2ng 16 gi\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch qu\u1ed1c gia V\u0110QG Vi\u1ec7t Nam 2018 h\u00f4m nay. Th\u00f4ng tin k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ghi b\u00e0n, clip b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, video highlights t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn ch\u00ednh tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u HAGL Ho\u00e0ng Anh Gia Lai vs Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh v\u00f2ng 16 V-League 2018 18h00 t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 26/6.</h2>K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 HAGL vs Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh: 4-0<br>\r\nNg\u01b0\u1eddi ghi b\u00e0n: V\u0103n To\u00e0n (3', 41'), C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng (43'), Ho\u00e0ng Thanh T\u00f9ng (90'+4)<br>\r\n<hr>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/6/26/HAGL-phut-44.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\">\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/6/26/HAGL-4-0-Quang-Ninh.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 0-3 \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 HAGL \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ea7y t\u1ef1 tin khi ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 Pleiku. V\u00e0 ngay ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 3, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 sau pha tho\u00e1t xu\u1ed1ng r\u1ea5t nhanh c\u1ee7a V\u0103n To\u00e0n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng n\u00e0y, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u1ea3i D\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ec3 tho\u00e1t kh\u1ecfi s\u1ef1 truy c\u1ea3n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi tung ra c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ee7 hi\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Tu\u1ea5n Linh trong t\u1ee9 th\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00e0n th\u1eafng s\u1edbm gi\u00fap c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 HAGL tr\u1edf n\u00ean t\u1ef1 tin h\u01a1n trong khi Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh l\u1ea1i g\u1eb7p r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n trong vi\u1ec7c ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn khung th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng. B\u00e0n g\u1ee1 c\u00f2n ch\u01b0a th\u1ea5y \u0111\u00e2u, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ea5t M\u1ecf su\u00fdt ch\u00fat n\u1eefa \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn b\u00e0n thua th\u1ee9 hai v\u1eabn xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t t\u1eeb s\u1ef1 b\u1ee9t t\u1ed1c c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o V\u0103n To\u00e0n.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HAGL vs Quang Ninh\" title=\"HAGL vs Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/26/ket-qua-hagl-vs-quang-ninh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>HAGL c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eadm tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede pha b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y, V\u0103n To\u00e0n \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n th\u1eafng trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 v\u1edbi D\u01b0\u01a1ng V\u0103n H\u00e0o bu\u1ed9c h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y ph\u1ea3i ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i d\u1eabn t\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c b\u1ecb tru\u1ea5t quy\u1ec1n thi \u0111\u1ea5u. D\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng t\u1eeb qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t sau \u0111\u00f3 nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf ch\u01a1i h\u01a1n ng\u01b0\u1eddi, kh\u00f4ng kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 &ldquo;G\u1ed7&rdquo; ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c l\u00e0m ch\u1ee7 th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u00eam hai b\u00e0n th\u1eafng n\u1eefa do c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a V\u0103n To\u00e0n \u1edf ph\u00fat 41 v\u00e0 C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf ph\u00fat 43.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf ghi 3 b\u00e0n trong hi\u1ec7p 1 l\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i h\u01a1n ng\u01b0\u1eddi, CLB HAGL \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t hi\u1ec7p 2 v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i. Do \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eafng qu\u00e1 \u0111\u1eadm n\u00ean HAGL ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng ch\u01a1i ch\u1eadm l\u1ea1i sau gi\u1edd ngh\u1ec9 gi\u1ea3i lao.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh c\u0169ng ch\u1eb3ng d\u00e1m n\u1eafm b\u1eaft l\u1ea5y th\u1eddi c\u01a1 d\u00e2ng cao b\u1edfi \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 10 ng\u01b0\u1eddi tr\u00ean s\u00e2n. N\u1ebfu qu\u00e1 m\u1ea3i m\u00ea t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng th\u00ec nguy c\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ea5t M\u1ecf b\u1ecb th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi th\u00eam l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn.&nbsp;<o:p></o:p>M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, v\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ea7m b\u00f3ng t\u1ed1t, CLB HAGL v\u1eabn l\u00e0m ch\u1ee7 th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn v\u00e0 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng pha t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng h\u01b0\u1edbng v\u1ec1 khung th\u00e0nh th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Tu\u1ea5n Linh. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1edbi ph\u00fat 57, V\u0103n To\u00e0n ch\u00fat n\u1eefa l\u1eadp \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c hattrick n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh ph\u00e1 b\u00f3ng ra tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u1ea1ch v\u1ed9i v\u00e0 Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tung ra c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1 b\u1ed3i t\u1ed1t.&nbsp;<o:p></o:p>\u00cdt ph\u00fat sau \u0111\u00f3, c\u1ea3 Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m tuy nhi\u00ean c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat sau \u0111\u00f3, tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u di\u1ec5n ra v\u1edbi t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 kh\u00e1 ch\u1eadm. C\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 HAGL mi\u1ec7t m\u00e0i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u00eam b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, trong khi \u0111\u00f3 Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh c\u0169ng su\u00fdt ch\u00fat n\u1eefa \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng danh d\u1ef1 tuy nhi\u00ean c\u00fa s\u00fat c\u1ee7a Nghi\u00eam Xu\u00e2n T\u00fa l\u1ea1i \u0111i tr\u00fang x\u00e0 ngang khung th\u00e0nh V\u0103n Ti\u1ebfn.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u01b0\u1edfng nh\u01b0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1ebd kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 3-0 th\u00ec \u0111\u00fang \u1edf ph\u00fat b\u00f9 gi\u1edd cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 v\u00e0o thay ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ho\u00e0ng Thanh T\u00f9ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 pha b\u1ee9t t\u1ed1c c\u1ef1c nhanh tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m ch\u00e9o g\u00f3c l\u00e0m rung l\u01b0\u1edbi khung th\u00e0nh Tu\u1ea5n Linh th\u00eam m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1eafng chung cu\u1ed9c 4-0, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea3 xong m\u00f3n n\u1ee3 thua 0-3 \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, h\u1ecd c\u0169ng v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 6 tr\u00ean BXH v\u1edbi 23 \u0111i\u1ec3m sau 16 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Minh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3840","checkdouble":"189647"},{"date":"19:16 26/06","title":"\u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam g\u1eb7p b\u1ea5t l\u1ee3i khi b\u1ecb x\u1ebfp v\u00e0o nh\u00f3m h\u1ea1t gi\u1ed1ng th\u1ea5p t\u1ea1i ASIAD","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/26/dt-olympic-viet-nam-gap-bat-loi-khi-bi-xep-vao-nhom-hat-giong-thap-tai-asiad.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, H\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ed3ng Olympic ch\u00e2u \u00c1 (OCA) \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdp k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 nh\u00f3m h\u1ea1t gi\u1ed1ng c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 th\u1eddi gian b\u1ed1c th\u0103m chia b\u1ea3ng m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018. V\u00e0 \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 n\u1eb1m \u1edf b\u1ea3ng t\u1eed th\u1ea7n khi b\u1ecb x\u1ebfp \u1edf nh\u00f3m 3.\r\n\r\n</h2><h2>\u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam g\u1eb7p b\u1ea5t l\u1ee3i khi n\u1eb1m \u1edf nh\u00f3m 3</h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng t\u1ea1i VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 v\u1edbi ng\u00f4i \u00e1 qu\u00e2n, HLV Park Hang Seo v\u00e0 c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u1eb7t h\u00e1i th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng t\u1ea1i m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam ASIAD 2018 - s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i v\u1ed1n d\u00e0nh cho c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 U23 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung 3 g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t ngo\u00e0i \u0111\u1ed9 tu\u1ed5i 23.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><em><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam g\u1eb7p b\u1ea5t l\u1ee3i khi b\u1ecb x\u1ebfp v\u00e0o nh\u00f3m h\u1ea1t gi\u1ed1ng th\u1ea5 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam g\u1eb7p b\u1ea5t l\u1ee3i khi b\u1ecb x\u1ebfp v\u00e0o nh\u00f3m h\u1ea1t gi\u1ed1ng th\u1ea5 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/26/u23-vietnam_ep0r479u5w6d1n97ckg00hkcj.jpg\"></em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>\u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam b\u1ecb x\u1ebfp v\u00e0o nh\u00f3m h\u1ea1t gi\u1ed1ng th\u1ee9 3 t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch n\u00e0y \u0111ang \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n khi Vi\u1ec7t Nam b\u1ecb x\u1ebfp v\u00e0o nh\u00f3m h\u1ea1t gi\u1ed1ng th\u1ee9 3 \u1edf gi\u1ea3i l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y sau bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdp k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y c\u1ee7a H\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ed3ng Olympic ch\u00e2u \u00c1 (OCA).\u00a0<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p>V\u1edbi k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 n\u00e0y, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ea1nh ngay t\u1eeb v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng. <o:p></o:p>\u1ede nh\u00f3m h\u1ea1t gi\u1ed1ng th\u1ee9 3, ngo\u00e0i Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f2n c\u00f3 3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 kh\u00e1c l\u00e0 Malaysia, L\u00e0o v\u00e0 Philippines. 4 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00e1c c\u0169ng n\u1eb1m \u1edf nh\u00f3m n\u00e0y l\u00e0 Jordan, Yemen, Bangladesh v\u00e0 H\u1ed3ng K\u00f4ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u00f3m 1 s\u1ebd g\u1ed3m c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n \u01b0u t\u00fa nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c g\u1ed3m nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n, Syria, Uzbekistan, \u1ea2 R\u1eadp X\u00ea \u00dat, Iran, Iraq c\u00f9ng ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Indonesia.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">8 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u1edf nh\u00f3m 2 bao g\u1ed3m Olympic Trung Qu\u1ed1c, Tri\u1ec1u Ti\u00ean, Oman, Qatar, Bahrain, UAE, Kyrgyzstan v\u00e0 Th\u00e1i Lan.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, nh\u00f3m h\u1ea1t gi\u1ed1ng th\u1ea5p nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i ASIAD l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y g\u1ed3m Nepal, \u1ea4n \u0110\u1ed9, Campuchia, \u0110\u00f4ng Timor, Tajikistan, Singapore, Myanmar v\u00e0 Palestine. \u00a0<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">32 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1ebd chia th\u00e0nh 8 b\u1ea3ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi th\u1ec3 th\u1ee9c t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 VCK World Cup \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ecdn ra 16 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng knock-out. L\u1ec5 b\u1ed1c th\u0103m chia b\u1ea3ng s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 15/07, trong khi \u0111\u00f3 m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam s\u1ebd b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1eeb ng\u00e0y 14/08/2018.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-tu-choi-sang-nga-xem-world-cup-vi-dai-cuc-168-189362.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/16/hlv-park-hang-seo-tu-choi-sang-nga-xem-world-cup-vi-dai-cuc.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-tu-choi-sang-nga-xem-world-cup-vi-dai-cuc-168-189362.html\">HLV Park Hang Seo t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i sang Nga xem World Cup v\u00ec \u0111\u1ea1i c\u1ee5c</span><br>\r\nTheo chia s\u1ebb m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y t\u1eeb T\u1ed5ng th\u01b0 k\u00fd VFF L\u00ea Ho\u00e0i Anh th\u00ec HLV Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng sang Nga xem World Cup theo l\u1eddi m\u1eddi tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 m\u00e0 \u00f4ng s\u1ebd d\u00e0nh th\u1eddi gian chu\u1ea9n...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-chi-dich-danh-3-cau-thu-co-the-lo-hen-voi-asiad-2018-168-187949.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/20/hlv-park-hang-seo-chi-dich-danh-3-cau-thu-co-the-lo-hen-voi-asiad-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-chi-dich-danh-3-cau-thu-co-the-lo-hen-voi-asiad-2018-168-187949.html\">HLV Park Hang Seo ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u00edch danh 3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u1ee1 h\u1eb9n v\u1edbi ASIAD 2018</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng, HLV Park Hang Seo cho r\u1eb1ng c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00ean h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf nh\u1eefng ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/goc-nhin-thay-park-se-cham-van-lam-hay-bui-tien-dung-cho-asiad-2018-168-187794.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/5/goc-nhin-thay-park-se-cham-van-lam-hay-bui-tien-dung-cho-asiad-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/goc-nhin-thay-park-se-cham-van-lam-hay-bui-tien-dung-cho-asiad-2018-168-187794.html\">G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn: Th\u1ea7y Park s\u1ebd ch\u1ea5m V\u0103n L\u00e2m hay B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng cho ASIAD 2018?</span><br>\r\n\u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m v\u00e0 B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng \u0111ang l\u00e0 hai th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n thi \u0111\u1ea5u n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam. Nh\u01b0ng li\u1ec7u HLV Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd ch\u1ecdn ai b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh cho \u0110T Olympic...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nguyen-tien-linh-manh-ghep-con-thieu-cua-thay-park-168-187368.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/30/nguyen-tien-linh-manh-ghep-con-thieu-cua-thay-park.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nguyen-tien-linh-manh-ghep-con-thieu-cua-thay-park-168-187368.html\">Nguy\u1ec5n Ti\u1ebfn Linh: M\u1ea3nh gh\u00e9p c\u00f2n thi\u1ebfu c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y Park?</span><br>\r\n\u0110i v\u00e0o l\u1ecbch s\u1eed v\u1edbi t\u01b0 c\u00e1ch l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb tu\u1ed5i nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1o m\u1ed9t c\u00fa poker b\u00e0n th\u1eafng t\u1ea1i V-League, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o tr\u1ebb Nguy\u1ec5n Ti\u1ebfn Linh \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u l\u1eddi khen t\u1eeb gi\u1edbi...</div>\r\n</div>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)</div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3839","checkdouble":"189648"},{"date":"20:01 26/06","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 26/6: MU nh\u1eadn c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi v\u1ee5 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2016/12/21/diem-tin-bong-da-toi-266-mu-nhan-cau-tra-loi-vu-hau-ve-35-trieu-bang.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd trong ph\u1ea7n \u0111i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u00ean chuy\u00ean trang Bongda24h t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 26/6.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">MU nh\u1eadn c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi v\u1ee5 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 266 MU nh\u1eadn c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi v\u1ee5 Jose Gaya h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 266 MU nh\u1eadn c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi v\u1ee5 Jose Gaya h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/15/Diem-tin-bong-da-toi-266-MU-nhan-cau-tra-loi-vu-Jose-Gaya-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Valencia tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n Jose Gaya cho M.U</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nTheo Don Balon, Valencia kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u00e1i Jose Gaya cho M.U. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1995.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Barca chi 80 tri\u1ec7u euro mua Milinkovic-Savic</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo Mundo Deportivo, Barca \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch h\u1ecfi mua ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Mundo Deportivo c\u1ee7a Lazio, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 80 tri\u1ec7u euro cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/barca-bat-ngo-muon-chi-80-trieu-euro-mua-pogba-serbia-180-189646.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/9/barca-bat-ngo-muon-chi-80-trieu-euro-mua-pogba-serbia.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/barca-bat-ngo-muon-chi-80-trieu-euro-mua-pogba-serbia-180-189646.html\">Barca b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd mu\u1ed1n chi 80 tri\u1ec7u euro mua Pogba Serbia</span><br>\r\nBarca mu\u1ed1n mua Sergej Milinkovic-Savic, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 80 tri\u1ec7u euro cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>MU mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ed5i Pogba l\u1ea5y Verratti</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo The Sun, \u0111\u1ec3 nu\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng s\u1edf h\u1eefu ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7&nbsp; Marco Verratti, M.U ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn hy sinh ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Paul Pogba. Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf mu\u1ed1n trao \u0111\u1ed5i ngang gi\u1eefa c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p v\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao 26 tu\u1ed5i ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Barca mu\u1ed1n mua l\u1ea1i Thiago Alcantara</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thiago Alcantara dinh chan thuong nghiem trong\" title=\"Thiago Alcantara d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/11/23/real-madrid-nham-nguoi-cu-barca-nang-cap-tuyen-giua.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Barca mu\u1ed1n mua l\u1ea1i Thiago Alcantara</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo Don Balon, Barca mu\u1ed1n mua l\u1ea1i ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Thiago Alcantara, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Bayern Munich. \u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 60 tri\u1ec7u euro cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1991.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Inter k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Nainggolan t\u1eeb Roma</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Inter Milan \u0111\u00e3 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Radja Nainggolan t\u1eeb Roma, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Milan \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn th\u00f4ng tin n\u00e0y.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>HLV Sarri s\u1eafp k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Chelsea</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo Mirror, Chelsea s\u1ebd b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m HLV Maurizio Sarri trong 48 gi\u1edd t\u1edbi, ngay sau \u0111\u00f3 h\u1ecd s\u1ebd c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 31 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mang t\u00ean Daniele Rugani t\u1eeb Juventus.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Juventus ch\u1ed1t gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n Alex Sandro</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo Sport Mediaset, Juventus s\u1ebd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn b\u00e1n h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Alex Sandro v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 52.8 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, hi\u1ec7n M.U v\u00e0 Chelsea mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 27 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Arsenal kh\u00f4ng mua Lewis Dunk</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Arsenal muon mua Lewis Dunk\" title=\"Arsenal mu\u1ed1n mua Lewis Dunk\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/26/arsenal-nham-sao-brighton-nang-cap-hang-thu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Arsenal t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i mua Lewis Dunk</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo Mirror, Arsenal s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng mua h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Lewis Dunk c\u1ee7a Brighton. HLV Unai Emery kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh, \u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n chuy\u1ec3n sang nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau kh\u00e1c thay v\u00ec chi 22 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Brighton.<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/arsenal-nham-sao-brighton-nang-cap-hang-thu-172-189633.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/26/arsenal-nham-sao-brighton-nang-cap-hang-thu.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/arsenal-nham-sao-brighton-nang-cap-hang-thu-172-189633.html\">Th\u1ef1c h\u01b0 v\u1ee5 Arsenal nh\u1eafm sao Brighton n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7</span><br>\r\nKh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Arsenal mua Lewis Dunk th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng cao. Theo Mirror, HLV Unai Emery kh\u00f4ng h\u1ee9ng th\u00fa v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 chuy\u1ec3n sang nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n Loftus-Cheek&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">The Telegraph kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Chelsea s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Ruben Loftus-Cheek, m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho Crystal Palace theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3838","checkdouble":"189651"},{"date":"18:26 26/06","title":"Barca b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd mu\u1ed1n chi 80 tri\u1ec7u euro mua \"Pogba Serbia\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/9/barca-bat-ngo-muon-chi-80-trieu-euro-mua-pogba-serbia.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Barca mu\u1ed1n mua Sergej Milinkovic-Savic, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 80 tri\u1ec7u euro cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Barca mu\u1ed1n t\u00ecm ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf Iniesta</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTi\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Iniesta \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh chia tay Barca sau nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3, s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn n\u01a1i tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Barca mu\u1ed1n mua Sergej Milinkovic-Savic v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 80 tri\u1ec7u euro h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Barca mu\u1ed1n mua Sergej Milinkovic-Savic v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 80 tri\u1ec7u euro h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/21/Barca-muon-mua-Sergej-Milinkovic-Savic-voi-gia-80-trieu-euro-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Barca t\u00ecm ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay Iniesta\u00a0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nHLV Ernesto Valverde \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf Iniesta. Don Balon kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalan \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi Christian Eriksen c\u1ee7a Tottenham ho\u1eb7c Miralem Pjanic c\u1ee7a Juventus, song nh\u1eefng th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng \u0111em l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng t\u00edn hi\u1ec7u kh\u1ea3 quan.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTottenham v\u00e0 Juventus \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n Eriksen v\u00e0 Pjanic c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i. Song song v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 hai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y, Barca \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eafm \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau kh\u00e1c.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Barca quan t\u00e2m Sergej Milinkovic-Savic</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo Mundo Deportivo, Barca mu\u1ed1n mua Sergej Milinkovic-Savic c\u1ee7a Lazio \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018. HLV Valverde \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Serbia v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n Barca \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n \u0111\u01b0a anh v\u1ec1 Camp Nou.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Milinkovic-Savic\" title=\"Milinkovic-Savic\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/9/barca-bat-ngo-muon-chi-80-trieu-euro-mua-pogba-serbia.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Barca quan t\u00e2m Milinkovic-Savic</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1995 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Lazio, anh ghi t\u1edbi 12 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1edf Serie A. Milinkovic-Savic \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 r\u1ea5t \u0111a n\u0103ng, anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ph\u00e2n ph\u1ed1i b\u00f3ng, chuy\u1ec1n d\u00e0i, ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o v\u00e0 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ec1u t\u1ed1t.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed do Iniesta \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/mu-gia-nhap-cuoc-dua-gianh-hang-hot-serie-a-172-174713.html\" target=\"_blank\">MU c\u0169ng quan t\u00e2m Milinkovic-Savic</span>, song nhi\u1ec1u ngu\u1ed3n tin cho r\u1eb1ng Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u00e3 r\u00fat lui trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y v\u00ec kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n m\u00e0 Lazio y\u00eau c\u1ea7u.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nBarca d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh chi ra 80 tri\u1ec7u euro cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Serbia, song s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd b\u1ecb Lazio t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf c\u0169ng chi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Italia nhanh ch\u00f3ng kh\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1eeb.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nLazio \u0111\u00f2i \u0111\u1ee7 100 tri\u1ec7u euro cho ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, n\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n nu\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng c\u00f3 Milinkovic-Savic Barca s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i chi \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n k\u1ec3 tr\u00ean.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3837","checkdouble":"189646"},{"date":"23:49 26/06","title":"Kaka x\u00fai Neymar b\u1ecf PSG gia nh\u1eadp Real Madrid","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/24/kaka-xui-neymar-bo-psg-gia-nhap-real-madrid.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u1ef1u danh th\u1ee7 Brazil l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng khuy\u00ean \u0111\u00e0n em \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u00ean s\u1edbm gia nh\u1eadp Real Madrid n\u1ebfu \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u anh th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 mong mu\u1ed1n.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Neymar s\u1edbm b\u1ecb \u0111\u1eb7t d\u1ea5u h\u1ecfi ch\u1ec9 sau v\u1ecfn v\u1eb9n m\u1ed9t n\u0103m ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi 222 tri\u1ec7u Euro sang Paris Saint-Germain. \u0110\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p kh\u00f4ng cao c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ph\u00e1p hay nh\u1eefng v\u1ee5 l\u00f9m x\u00f9m nh\u01b0 m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i, ng\u00f4i sao Brazil ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ra \u0111i ngay \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018 n\u00e0y.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Neymar c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 Barcelona nh\u01b0ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t c\u00fa s\u1ed1c kh\u00f4ng t\u01b0\u1edfng, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 vi\u1ec7c anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gia nh\u1eadp \u0111\u1ea1i k\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ecbch Real Madrid m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng m\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ebfn c\u01a1n b\u00e3o t\u1ed1 th\u1ecbnh n\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb c\u00e1c Cules. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Kaka khuy\u00ean Neymar gia nh\u1eadp Real Madrid chia tay PSG h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Kaka khuy\u00ean Neymar gia nh\u1eadp Real Madrid chia tay PSG h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/24/kaka-xui-neymar-bo-psg-gia-nhap-real-madrid.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Kaka khuy\u00ean Neymar gia nh\u1eadp Real Madrid</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Tr\u00ean th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, ch\u00ednh CLB ho\u00e0ng gia T\u00e2y Ban Nha m\u1edbi l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 t\u1eeb thu\u1edf nh\u1ecf c\u1ee7a Neymar v\u00e0 gi\u1edd \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i n\u00e2ng cao v\u1ecb th\u1ebf v\u00e0 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh, danh ti\u1ebfng thay th\u1ebf ch\u00ednh nh\u1eefng Cristiano Ronaldo hay Gareth Bale, ng\u00f4i sao Brazil kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m ng\u01a1.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec v\u1eady m\u00e0 Kaka khuy\u00ean Neymar gia nh\u1eadp Real Madrid theo ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y nh\u1ea5t. C\u1ef1u ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 h\u00e0o hoa \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 \u0111\u00e0n em \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng s\u1edbm c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 c\u1ee7a anh, m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 n\u00f3 \u0111em \u0111\u1ebfn cho anh nhi\u1ec1u k\u1ef7 ni\u1ec7m bu\u1ed3n h\u01a1n vui.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Kaka cho bi\u1ebft: \u201c\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Neymar v\u00e0 t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y n\u00ean can \u0111\u1ea3m quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh theo nh\u1eefng g\u00ec m\u00ecnh mu\u1ed1n. N\u1ebfu ra \u0111i th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta s\u1ebd n\u00f3i r\u1eb1ng Neymar gia nh\u1eadp PSG ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 x\u00e2y c\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ebfn Real Madrid.\u201d <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201c\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn v\u00ec nh\u1eefng g\u00ec t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t cho b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n, trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p n\u00e0y theo t\u00f4i l\u00e0 c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Bernabeu. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 26 tu\u1ed5i v\u00e0 \u0111ang \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9 ch\u00edn \u1edf c\u1ea3 chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n v\u00e0 t\u00e2m l\u00fd c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7. Th\u1ebf n\u00ean th\u1ee9 Neymar c\u1ea7n l\u00fac n\u00e0y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t CLB v\u0129 \u0111\u1ea1i s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00ean \u0111\u1ec9nh cao, nh\u01b0 Real Madrid.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/barca-muon-so-huu-dong-doi-cua-neymar-sau-world-cup-2018-172-189666.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/28/barca-muon-so-huu-dong-doi-cua-neymar-sau-world-cup-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/barca-muon-so-huu-dong-doi-cua-neymar-sau-world-cup-2018-172-189666.html\">Barca mu\u1ed1n s\u1edf h\u1eefu \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a Neymar sau World Cup 2018</span><br>\r\nTheo truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng T\u00e2y Ban Nha, CLB Barca \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Gabriel Jesus c\u1ee7a Man City trong  k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3836","checkdouble":"189667"},{"date":"20:14 26/06","title":"Liverpool ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 s\u1ef1 th\u1ef1c \u0111au l\u00f2ng t\u1eeb Sturridge","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/1/10/liverpool-tiet-lo-su-thuc-dau-long-tu-sturridge.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Liverpool b\u00e1n Daniel Sturridge \u0111ang r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n, \u0111\u00edch th\u00e2n \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Anfield x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o h\u1ecfi mua ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Liverpool s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1n Daniel Sturridge v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 15 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nD\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV Klopp, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Daniel Sturridge kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0o l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Liverpool. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, khi kh\u1ecfe m\u1ea1nh anh ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Liverpool b\u00e1n Daniel Sturridge nh\u01b0ng ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o h\u1ecfi mua h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Liverpool b\u00e1n Daniel Sturridge nh\u01b0ng ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o h\u1ecfi mua h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/1/26/Liverpool-ban-Daniel-Sturridge-nhung-chua-doi-bong-nao-hoi-mua-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Liverpool ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn b\u00e1n Sturridge v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 15 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nSturridge l\u00e0 m\u1eabu trung phong c\u1eafm truy\u1ec1n th\u1ed1ng, anh ch\u1ec9 quanh qu\u1ea9n trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00f3n b\u00f3ng t\u1eeb c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i. HLV Klopp kh\u00f4ng \u01b0a th\u00edch m\u1eabu ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o n\u00e0y, \u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0o l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i chung c\u1ee7a to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nCh\u00ednh v\u00ec v\u1eady Sturridge b\u1ecb m\u1ea5t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed v\u00e0o tay Roberto Firmino. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 1 n\u0103m nay anh c\u00f2n b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea9y t\u1edbi West Brom theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p g\u00ec nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0o l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a The Kop, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 C\u1ea3ng \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y ra \u0111i \u1edf H\u00e8 2018. Daily Mail kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/liverpool-chot-gia-ban-sturridge-voi-gia-beo-172-188935.html\" target=\"_blank\">Liverpool b\u00e1n Daniel Sturridge</span> v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 15 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o h\u1ecfi mua Daniel Sturridge</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo nhi\u1ec1u ngu\u1ed3n tin c\u00f3 \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u1edf Anh mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Daniel Sturridge, theo \u0111\u00f3 Newcastle, Southampton v\u00e0 West Ham mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 ch\u00e2n s\u00fat sinh n\u0103m 1989, h\u1ecd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi \u0111\u1ee7 15 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng nh\u01b0 ph\u00eda Liverpool y\u00eau c\u1ea7u.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Liverpool b\u00e1n Daniel Sturridge nh\u01b0ng ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o h\u1ecfi mua h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Liverpool b\u00e1n Daniel Sturridge nh\u01b0ng ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o h\u1ecfi mua h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/1/10/liverpool-tiet-lo-su-thuc-dau-long-tu-sturridge.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o h\u1ecfi mua Sturridge</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, Liverpool b\u00e1n Daniel Sturridge \u0111ang r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n, \u0111\u00edch th\u00e2n \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Anfield x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o h\u1ecfi mua ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o g\u1eedi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i, nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n l\u00e0 m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u00ean t\u1edbi 150.000 b\u1ea3ng/tu\u1ea7n m\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111ang h\u01b0\u1edfng khi\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u1ea7m trung kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nN\u1ebfu Sturridge \u0111ang kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn gi\u1ea3m l\u01b0\u01a1ng s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 anh tho\u00e1t kh\u1ecfi Anfield. Ng\u00f4i sao 29 tu\u1ed5i s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn: Ho\u1eb7c gi\u1ea3m l\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra \u0111i ho\u1eb7c \u1edf l\u1ea1i nh\u01b0ng ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3835","checkdouble":"189649"},{"date":"20:28 26/06","title":"MU gia nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua gi\u00e0nh sao Real Madrid","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/7/mu-gia-nhap-cuoc-dua-gianh-sao-real-madrid.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>MU mu\u1ed1n mua Mateo Kovacic, theo Don Balon, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Mateo Kovacic \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Real Madrid</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nT\u1eeb khi \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho Real Madrid ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Mateo Kovacic ch\u01b0a khi n\u00e0o tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 quan tr\u1ecdng trong l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Los Blancos. C\u1ef1u sao Inter Milan ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1eeb b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"MU mu\u1ed1n mua Mateo Kovacic v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"MU mu\u1ed1n mua Mateo Kovacic v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/2/MU-muon-mua-Mateo-Kovacic-voi-gia-35-trieu-bang-o-He-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\u00a0Kovacic mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Real Madrid \u1edf H\u00e8 2018</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Kroos v\u00e0 Modric v\u1eabn \u0111ang ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t \u1edf tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa, Kovacic \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.\u00a0</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nVi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean khi\u1ebfn ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1994 c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng, anh \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Bernabeu \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1\u00a0ch\u00ednh nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u00edch th\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Kovacic x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn ng\u00f4i sao 24 tu\u1ed5i s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng r\u1eddi Real \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 n\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb h\u1ee3p l\u00fd.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cN\u0103m nay c\u1eadu \u1ea5y 24 tu\u1ed5i, Kovacic mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb \u1edf Bernabeu. N\u1ebfu c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o \u0111\u01b0a ra m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb h\u1ee3p l\u00fd ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n\u201d.</div>\r\n<h2>MU h\u1ecfi mua Kovacic</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Bi\u1ebft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00f4ng tin ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Real Madrid, nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 24 tu\u1ed5i. Mirror kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/lo-ben-do-moi-cua-mateo-kovacic-180-189349.html\" target=\"_blank\">Tottenham mu\u1ed1n mua Kovacic</span>, h\u1ecd nh\u1eafm c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1994 thay Dembele.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Real vs PSG Kovacic\" title=\"Real vs PSG Kovacic\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/7/mu-gia-nhap-cuoc-dua-gianh-sao-real-madrid.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>MU nh\u1ea3y v\u00e0o cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua gi\u00e0nh Kovacic</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, Theo Don Balon, MU mu\u1ed1n mua Mateo Kovacic, Mourinho \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia v\u00e0 nh\u1eafm anh thay th\u1ebf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed do Carrick \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y M.U ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi ra 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, ngo\u00e0i ra Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf c\u00f2n ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng 200.000 b\u1ea3ng/tu\u1ea7n cho ng\u00f4i sao 24 tu\u1ed5i.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng t\u1eeb M.U \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn Real Madrid h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng. HLV Lopetegui hi\u1ec7n \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch t\u00ecm ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf Kovacic, nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf c\u00f3 ngh\u0129a l\u00e0 Los Blancos \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 24 tu\u1ed5i ra \u0111i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKovacic \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1eabu ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m kh\u00e1 to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n, anh c\u00f3 s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng tranh ch\u1ea5p kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1994 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng trong m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh, Kovacic s\u1ebd l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho Man \u0111\u1ecf.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3834","checkdouble":"189650"},{"date":"20:50 26/06","title":"Marco Asensio c\u00f3 c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi cho Liverpool","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/26/marco-asensio-co-cau-tra-loi-cho-liverpool.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Marco Asensio ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh mu\u1ed1n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi Real Madrid thay v\u00ec chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Liverpool.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Liverpool chi 180 tri\u1ec7u euro mua Marco Asensio</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 1 v\u1eeba qua, Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u1eef ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Coutinho tr\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1ef1 ch\u00e8o k\u00e9o t\u1eeb Barca. The Kop thu v\u1ec1 160 tri\u1ec7u euro t\u1eeb ti\u1ec1n b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Marco Asensio ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Marco Asensio ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/26/Marco-Asensio-phat-bieu-ve-tuong-lai-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Liverpool chi \u0111\u1eadm mua Marco Asensio\u00a0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nHLV Klopp kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u00f4ng s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 thay th\u1ebf Coutinho \u1edf H\u00e8 2018. Mirror kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/xac-nhan-liverpool-hoi-mua-asensio-nhung-khong-thanh-cong-172-164802.html\" target=\"_blank\"> Liverpool quan t\u00e2m Marco Asensio</span>, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Anfield ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi t\u1edbi 180 tri\u1ec7u euro cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Klopp \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 c\u1ef1c cao ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1996, \u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n BL\u0110 The Kop c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 22 tu\u1ed5i.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, Asensio \u0111\u00e3 tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh v\u01b0\u1ee3t b\u1eadc, anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNg\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi TBN s\u1edf h\u1eefu nh\u1eefng t\u1ed1 ch\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9, k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng qua ng\u01b0\u1eddi, ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o v\u00e0 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m. V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng t\u1ed1 ch\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 22 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c\u00a0 cho l\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Asensio c\u00f3 c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi cho Liverpool</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Marco Asensio ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh mu\u1ed1n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi Real Madrid thay v\u00ec chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Liverpool.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Marco Asensio ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Marco Asensio ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/26/marco-asensio-co-cau-tra-loi-cho-liverpool.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Asensio \u01b0u ti\u00ean \u1edf l\u1ea1i Real thay v\u00ec t\u1edbi Liverpool</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cSau World Cup, t\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u00f3 cu\u1ed9c n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi HLV Lopetegui, t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t vui khi \u00f4ng \u1ea5y \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Real Madrid. T\u00f4i c\u00f2n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Real v\u00e0 t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean mu\u1ed1n \u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y c\u00e0ng l\u00e2u c\u00e0ng t\u1ed1t, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 r\u1ea5t d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng khi ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n bi\u1ebft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch c\u1ee7a HLV m\u1edbi, t\u00f4i c\u0169ng hi\u1ec3u r\u1eb1ng m\u00ecnh ph\u1ea3i c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u n\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 mu\u1ed1n c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh. Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i t\u00f4i \u0111ang t\u1eadp trung cho World Cup 2018 c\u00f9ng \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3833","checkdouble":"189656"},{"date":"23:10 26/06","title":"Barca mu\u1ed1n s\u1edf h\u1eefu \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a Neymar sau World Cup 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/3/28/barca-muon-so-huu-dong-doi-cua-neymar-sau-world-cup-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Theo truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng T\u00e2y Ban Nha, CLB Barca \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Gabriel Jesus c\u1ee7a Man City trong  k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018.</h2><h2>Barca mu\u1ed1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Gabriel Jesus c\u1ee7a Man City</h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Antoine Griezmann sau khi ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p v\u1eeba \u0111\u1eb7t b\u00fat gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi CLB Atletico Madrid t\u1edbi n\u0103m 2022, Barca \u0111ang t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm nh\u1eefng g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t ti\u1ec1n n\u0103ng thay th\u1ebf anh. V\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Nou Camp \u0111\u1ec3 \u00fd ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao tr\u1ebb c\u1ee7a Man City, Gabriel Jesus.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Gabriel Jesus ghi ban mo ty so\" title=\"Gabriel Jesus ghi b\u00e0n m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/10/Truc-tiep-Ao-vs-Brazil-21h00-ngay-hom-nay-106-Giao-huu-quoc-te-hinh-anh.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Gabriel Jesus \u0111ang l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau theo \u0111u\u1ed5i h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Barca</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo nh\u1eadt b\u00e1o AS, s\u1edf d\u0129 Jesus r\u01a1i v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a Blaugrana l\u00e0 b\u1edfi c\u1ea3 HLV Ernesto Valverde v\u00e0 t\u00e2n G\u0110TT Eric Abidal \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 r\u1ea5t cao kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o 21 tu\u1ed5i n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi l\u1ed1i \u0111\u00e1 k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt nh\u01b0ng gi\u00e0u t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u00e1n l\u01b0\u1edbt, Jesus \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Barca v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp t\u1ed1t v\u00e0o h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd. T\u1ea1i Man xanh l\u00fac n\u00e0y, Jesus v\u1eabn \u0111ang ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea1nh tranh su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a City v\u1edbi Sergio Aguero. Do \u0111\u00f3 khi sang Barca c\u1eeda \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh c\u1ee7a anh s\u1ebd s\u00e1ng s\u1ee7a h\u01a1n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Gabriel Jesus v\u1edbi Man City c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n t\u1edbi n\u0103m 2021. M\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, d\u00f9 c\u00f3 giai \u0111o\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng tuy nhi\u00ean ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o \u0110T Brazil v\u1eabn k\u1ecbp ghi d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n v\u1edbi 17 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 5 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o cho \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n, n\u1ebfu thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Man City nh\u1ea3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, m\u1ee9c ph\u00ed \u0111\u1ec3 Barca s\u1edf h\u1eefu Gabriel Jesus ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng r\u1ebb. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00ec th\u1ebf trong th\u1eddi gian qua, nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 La Liga c\u0169ng \u0111ang h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi c\u00e1c m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau &lsquo;m\u1ec1m&rsquo; h\u01a1n nh\u01b0 Miralem Pjanic c\u1ee7a Juventus hay c\u00e1c ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang l\u00ean t\u1ea1i World Cup nh\u01b0 Herving Lozano c\u1ee7a Mexico hay Aleksandr Golovin c\u1ee7a Nga.&nbsp;<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/brazil-mat-hai-tru-cot-truoc-tran-gap-serbia-421-189658.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/23/brazil-mat-hai-tru-cot-truoc-tran-gap-serbia.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/brazil-mat-hai-tru-cot-truoc-tran-gap-serbia-421-189658.html\">Brazil m\u1ea5t hai tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Serbia</span><br>\r\nTheo tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, \u0110T Brazil s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a hai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t l\u00e0 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Danilo v\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh Douglas Costa \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Serbia v\u00ec...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hlv-sarri-muon-chelsea-chi-70-trieu-bang-mua-thu-mon-nguoi-brazil-172-189429.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/11/hlv-sarri-muon-chelsea-chi-70-trieu-bang-mua-thu-mon-nguoi-brazil.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hlv-sarri-muon-chelsea-chi-70-trieu-bang-mua-thu-mon-nguoi-brazil-172-189429.html\">HLV Sarri mu\u1ed1n Chelsea chi 70 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil</span><br>\r\nMaurizio Sarri mu\u1ed1n Chelsea mua Alisson c\u1ee7a Roma, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 Thibaut Courtois ra \u0111i qua \u0111\u00f3 d\u1ecdn \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u00f3n th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/3-yeu-to-quyet-dinh-tran-dau-brazil-20-costa-rica-421-189317.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/22/3-yeu-to-quyet-dinh-tran-dau-brazil-20-costa-rica.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/3-yeu-to-quyet-dinh-tran-dau-brazil-20-costa-rica-421-189317.html\">4 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Brazil 2-0 Costa Rica</span><br>\r\n\u0110T Brazil cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t Costa Rica thi \u0111\u1ea5u ngoan c\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi \u1edf nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i. V\u00e0 d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 4 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1...</div>\r\n</div>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3832","checkdouble":"189666"}]}